- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possibility as the paper deals with graph theory and the computation of connected components. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a potential category as the paper discusses the theoretical guarantees and running time of the algorithm. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with graph clustering and connected components, which are relevant to network analysis.
